overview: On December 16th The TrapHouse Fight Club makes its return to Los Angeles, CA for the aggressive, cinematic spectacular that event - it is "The World Is Yours" premiering worldwide on FITE.  The event features the Epic 1st Time Ever Encounter:  PCO vs 2 Cold Scorpio  Also in the lineup: Lio Rush, Joey Janela, JTG, Brian Cage, Jordan Oliver, Jimmy Jacobs, Jimmy Lloyd and many more.
title: VxS The World is Yours
